Arch Linux
==========

To build the package under Arch Linux, grab the package tarball from the current
release[1] (NEEDS UPDATE) or the latest git version[2] and build the package with makepkg[3].

[1] http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=31518
[2] https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/ansel-git
[3] https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Makepkg


To ease things you could also install paru or yay[4], which should automatically
download, build and install the package.

[4] https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/AUR_helpers
